title: Kep Enderby Memorial Lecture - Introductory Remarks (Australian Human Rights Commission)
text: ( Source : Australian Human Rights Commission ) Kep Enderby Memorial Lecture Sydney , 6pm, 22 October 2015 In a little over a week's time, the 31st of October will mark 40 years to the day that the Racial Discrimination Act came into effect.
